bilingual.source: We need to revise the initial design.
bilingual.target: 我们需要修改最初的设计。

bilingual.source: The initial idea was proposed by him.
bilingual.target: 最初的想法是由他提出的。

bilingual.source: His initial reaction was one of surprise.
bilingual.target: 他的最初的反应是惊讶。

bilingual.source: The project went beyond the initial budget.
bilingual.target: 这个项目超出了最初的预算。

bilingual.source: The manager decided to override the initial decision.
bilingual.target: 经理决定推翻最初的决定。

bilingual.source: The initial results of the experiment were promising.
bilingual.target: 实验的最初的结果很有希望。

bilingual.source: The initial test results showed everything was normal.
bilingual.target: 最初的测试结果显示一切正常。

bilingual.source: The initial investment was small, but it grew over time.
bilingual.target: 最初的投资很小，但随着时间的推移而增长。

bilingual.source: The initial meeting set the tone for the entire project.
bilingual.target: 最初的会议为整个项目定下了基调。

bilingual.source: The findings are associable with the initial hypothesis.
bilingual.target: 这些发现是可关联的，与最初的假设一致。

list.abstract: initial是复合式品牌，2000年创立，在国内拥有多家门店，分别位于香港、上海、厦门、深圳和成都等地。 2022年2月，initial品牌官方对消费者被initial官方旗舰店客服送花圈事件道歉并进行处理：涉事店铺闭店，涉事店员花圈下单的账号永久停封，涉事的员工做开除处理并公开道歉信。

yingyinNormal.en: And you've made your initial decision into a stream of decisions and into a habit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你最初的那个决定影响了此后你一连串的决定，最终它成为你的一个习惯。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, but the good news is that we're ready to go. We have a plan in place. We've done some initial polling.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，但好消息是我们已经准备好了，已经有了计划，也做了最初的民调。

yingyinNormal.en: Initial here to acknowledge you received it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里签首字母缩写，确认已拿钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: It'll also help improve her initial impression of you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这同时也能改善你在她心目中的最初印象。

yingyinNormal.en: The initial death toll will shake world governments to their core.
yingyinNormal.zh: 初期死亡人数足以震惊到世界政府的核心。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, gee. My initial reaction is no, but, you know, let me think about it and get back to you, okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 老天，我初步的建议是不要，让我想想再回答你吧？

yingyinNormal.en: They've put potentially habitable worlds right within our reach. Twelve, in fact, from our initial probes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们将宜居的世界，放在了我们触手可及的地方，十二个，这是我们初步探查的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: Just a few more signatures, and we'll be finished. Initial here to acknowledge that you've returned your key.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再签几个名，就大功告成了，这里签首字母缩写，确认已归还钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to bed. At least take this with you. Look, and have Stephanie initial here, here, here, here and here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去睡觉了。你至少也得把这带走吧。别忘了让斯蒂芬妮签名，这里，这里，这里，还有这里。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, and lastly, please initial here to confirm that ownership of the living room couch is hereby transferred to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，最后在这里签首字母来确认客厅沙发的所有权在此转让给我。

yingyinNormal.en: Does that really need to be in the agreement? We might as well settle it now; it's going to be on for years. Initial here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这条也要放到协议里啊？最好是现在定下来，那可要播好几年呢，在这里草签。

yingyinNormal.en: The same study found that those who didn't get the initial hormonal increase drug didn't see their hormone levels increase.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在同样的一项研究中发现，有部分没有服用真正荷尔蒙药物的人荷尔蒙并没有增加。

yingyinNormal.en: See, my initial approach to Kripke had the same deficiencies as those that plagued Stu the Cockatoo when he was new at the zoo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是这样，我最初和Kripke搭话就跟鹦鹉斯图刚到公园时一样有着缺陷。

yingyinNormal.en: Using fMRI, or functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging, researchers have identified an extended network of brain regions that respond to new information that's inconsistent with initial impressions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 透过 fMRI也就是功能性磁振造影，研究员指出有一块大脑区域延伸出的网络对于和第一印象不同的新信息会有反应。
